# LLM Strategy

The LLM is not the product.

The ontology is the product.

The LLM should be used only where reasoning is required.

Everything deterministic should happen before invoking the LLM.

Examples

Parser

Regex

NER

Embedding Search

Ontology Mapping

Vocabulary Matching

These should execute without the LLM.

